oo simple, sometimes naive."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T00:31:10.000Z","msg":"日本近年舔共<br />\n已有點睇唔起日本班官員<br />\n中共亦知晒架仔底細<br />\n滲透到無得剩"},{"pid":"b8418e1a58d77a75da8219508f682f816a553b0e","tid":2076817,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T00:33:42.000Z","msg":"東京想成為國際金融中心，先要有基本法"},{"pid":"5c584e5fc8a5fa40f739d3faed11801e2f70ab70","tid":2076817,"uid":159870,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T00:36:55.000Z","msg":"以為梁錦松。。。"},{"pid":"cc3f7ca06399aad2dccebb9e88057346ab93c7c9","tid":2076817,"uid":278783,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T00:43:58.000Z","msg":"成日覺得代表唔到香港呢d論述都好On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國際地位係外國比，憑咩代表人地決定地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c75c61d5d45fab4c479f12beee694224aa7b649","tid":2076817,"uid":196552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T00:45:36.000Z","msg":"日本最大問題係稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c01d96ff8bf0db2c1e68c06300291a37cb9d68a","tid":2076817,"uid":198175,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T00:56:37.000Z","msg":"10年前起, 香港已淪為支那的國際金融中心, 只為支那國家資本主義之利益服務, 而再非倫敦紐約新加坡同義的真國際金融中心<br />\n<br />\n東京如真能修改投資及稅務法規, 比起隨時會被支共入侵的台北, 又或是已受支共重大影響滲透嘅新加坡, 在國家實力及安全上更能吸引亞洲區嘅有錢佬將錢放在東京作財富管理<br />\n<br />\n而家香港正步入收皮期, 全球經濟強國都打香港人財的主意, 支共最好加大力度玩国安法全面管治, 加速香港財散人安樂嘅攬炒進程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4e6cf7c3254230bc95394ddcf42d58a8532861","tid":2076817,"uid":63108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c75c61d5d45fab4c479f12beee694224aa7b649","tid":2076817,"uid":196552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T00:45:36.000Z","msg":"日本最大問題係稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T00:56:56.000Z","msg":"最理想台灣或星狗（有合作過就知點解係狗）<img src